title: Kanye West releases two surprise songs
text: Kanye West releases two surprise songs Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) , Oct 18 (ANI): There's good news for all the Kanye West 's fans as the rapper has unexpectedly released two new songs 'When I See It' and 'Say You Will' to his SoundCloud. Kanye West Releases Two Songs On Soundcloud 00:41 As Kanye West has been teasing a new album over the past year, now out of the blue, he has put two new songs on SoundCloud.
